definitions.definition: Any of various current or former benefits or allowances paid by the Government to support the sick, disabled or incapacitated.
labels: especially in the phrases on the sick
label_groups: especially in the phrases on the sick and on long-term sick

secondary_definitions: ( British , colloquial ) (especially in the phrases on the sick and on long-term sick ) Any of various current or former benefits or allowances paid by the Government to support the sick, disabled or incapacitated.
